'''Corellian limpets''' were free-floating [[Parasite/Legends|parasites]] native to space near [[Corellia/Legends|Corellia]]. They were attracted to spilled fuel, but would feed upon whatever was available. On rare occasions they could attach themselves onto a living being and become permanently grafted to their victim's body.

